reviewText: Mike rocks the house! His sense of humor and ability to find the hilarious stuff that surrounds us everyday will bring you near tears laughing. And it's all clean comedy! Highly recommended!
Loved the DVD showed it to whole family it was great. Thinking of getting more from Bananas Comedy.
If you like music mixed in with comedy, this is the movie for you!

This guy is funny and I enjoyed most of his show but at times he comes off a little bitter.  The end of the show he gives his life story and that is worth the price you pay for this dvd.  Overall I thought he was very funny.
